-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":40362,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Zuhd: Renounce the worldly life, Allah will love you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa'd reported: A man came to the Prophet and said, \"O Messenger of Allah, tell me about a deed which will make Allah and people love me.\" The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRenounce the worldly life and Allah will love you. Renounce what people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31771,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/allah-protects-servants-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":40362,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Allah protects beloved servants from worldly life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah ibn al-Nu\u2019man reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Allah loves a servant, He protects them from the worldly life, just as one of you protects the sick from drinking too much water.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2036 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11322,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/10\/hiyat-al-dunya-almost-worthless\/","url_meta":{"origin":40362,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Worldly life is nearly worthless to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Eli